      "title": "Mano met the American ambassador",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Mano Ganesan, President of the Tamil Progressive Alliance, has met the US Ambassador to Sri Lanka.",
        "Mano Ganesan tweeted that they discussed about democracy, rule of law, anti-terrorism law, Tamil national issue, national economic crisis, diaspora Tamil issue, and the problems of the poor plantation people."
